import React from 'react'
import { Row, Col, Container } from 'react-bootstrap'
import Layout from '../../layouts/header.layout'
import './HomeStyle.css'
const Home = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Layout>
        <Container fluid>
          <Col md={2} className="sidebar">
            Sidebar
          </Col>
          <Col md={10} style={{ marginLeft: 'auto' }}>
            Container
          </Col>
        </Container>
      </Layout>
    </>
  )
}

export default Home
